  "description": "Persistent todo list for Pi. Track tasks across sessions with priorities, tags, and due dates.",
  "readme": "# pi-todo\n\nPersistent todo list for Pi. Track tasks across sessions with priorities and tags.\n\n## Install\n```bash\npi install npm:@artale/pi-todo\n```\n\n## Commands\n```\n/todo add <text> [--pri high|med|low] [--tag <t>]\n/todo list [--tag <t>] [--pri <p>]\n/todo done <id>\n/todo rm <id>\n/todo clear\n```\n\n## License\nMIT\n",
